belgian march consum price rise belgian consum price rose 0.11 pct in march from februari to stand 1.27 pct abov the level in march 1986 , the econom affair ministri said in a statement . it said the consum price index , base 1981 , rose to 132.83 point from 132.69 in februari and 131.17 in march 1985. year-on-year inflat stood at 1.00 pct in februari and at 1.53 pct in march 1986 .